<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hu">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Skyhigh AI | License Activation</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body { background: #050505; color: white; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        .pricing-card { background: rgba(15, 15, 15, 0.8); border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3); border-radius: 32px; backdrop-filter: blur(10px); }
        .neon-border { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-6">

    <div class="max-w-xl w-full">
        <div class="text-center mb-10">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-black italic tracking-tighter text-purple-500">SKYHIGH AI</h1>
            <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[5px] text-zinc-500 font-bold mt-2">Neural License Required</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-card p-8 md:p-12 neon-border">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-center">Aktiválja a hozzáférését</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm text-center mb-10">A robot használatához érvényes licencre és a kezdőtőke megadására van szükség.</p>

            <form action="/user/set-capital" method="POST" class="space-y-6">
                
                <div class="space-y-2">
                    <label class="text-[10px] uppercase font-black text-purple-500 tracking-widest ml-2">Kezdeti tőke (EUR / HUF)</label>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <i class="fas fa-wallet absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-zinc-600"></i>
                        <input type="number" name="capital" required 
                               class="w-full bg-black border border-white/10 rounded-2xl py-4 pl-12 pr-4 text-white font-bold focus:border-purple-500 outline-none transition"
                               placeholder="Pl. 1000">
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-[9px] text-zinc-600 italic ml-2">* A robot ezen összeg alapján számolja a napi profitot.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-purple-600/10 border border-purple-500/20 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-8">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-black italic text-lg uppercase">Full Neural Access</p>
                            <p class="text-xs text-purple-400">30 napos korlátlan hozzáférés</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-right">
                            <p class="text-2xl font-black">€49</p>
                            <p class="text-[9px] text-zinc-500 uppercase">Per Month</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white font-black py-5 rounded-2xl uppercase tracking-widest shadow-lg shadow-purple-600/30 transition transform hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-95">
                    Licenc Aktiválása és Belépés
                </button>

            </form>

            <div class="mt-8 text-center">
                <p class="text-[10px] text-zinc-600 uppercase tracking-widest">
                    Biztonságos fizetés és titkosított adatok
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
            <a href="/logout" class="text-xs text-zinc-700 hover:text-white transition uppercase font-bold tracking-widest">Kijelentkezés</a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>